These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-1::.
There 6 different types of food: grapefruit, lemon, plum, papaya, asparagus, peach
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, epic, superhero, western, zombie
 1. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
 2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 3. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is between the person eating asparagus and the person watching disaster movies##2
 5. the person watching western movies is the person eating plum##1
 6. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
 9. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
11. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4    |    5     |  6   |
| Food      | plum | papaya   | asparagus | grapefruit | lemon    | peach  |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | superhero | zombie   | crime  | disaster | epic |

