.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  paramedic, musician, entrepreneur, security-guard, analyst, fisherman
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, r&b, rock, soul, trance
 1. the fisherman is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 3. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the musician##1
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
 6. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 7. the paramedic is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 8. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 9. the fan of r&b is between the fisherman and the fan of trance##2
10. the fan of soul is on the right of the analyst##1
11. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Job      | fisherman | paramedic | analyst   | security-guard | musician   | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | r&b         | trance | soul     | dubstep | rock     |

