The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, drama, mystery, horror, western
 1. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
10. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| Beverage   | 7up     | cola     | fanta  | tea     | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy | western | drama | satire | mystery          | horror   |

