 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the colombian##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 9. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
10. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
11. the person who's birthday is in may is the american##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |       4       |    5    |       6       |
| Nationality   | mexican | turkish  | american | colombian     | chinese | polish        |
| Birthday         | april | january | may    | november | march  | august |

