 3. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
10. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in october##2
11. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
12. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
13. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
