.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-9::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, dahlia, sunflower, lily, balloon-flower
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, subway, tram, van
 1. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
 9. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsdahlia and the person driving the van##2
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
14. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
15. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
16. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |    3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |
| Flower   | sunflower | rose | lily | dahlia     | balloon-flower | marigold |
| Transport     | tram  | bike      | bus      | snowmobile | subway  | van    |

