 8. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
11. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
12. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
