 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is handball##1
13. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | water  | tea        | sprite  | fanta     | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Sport       | sailing | swimming | cycling | water-polo | handball  | rowing          |

