.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, almond-milk, water, sprite
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bus, car, motorbike, subway, taxi
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 9. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Beverage         | sprite    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea | juice    | water |
| Transport   | airplane | taxi  | subway | car      | motorbike | bus    |

 